{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all hospitality venues to provide large print and Braille menus",
        "additional_details": "This would help every establishment to become accessible for sight impaired / severely sight impaired people. At the moment, a lot of establishments do not provide a range of accessible formats. This can impact independence which in turn can deter people from attending. I appreciate others may be in the same situation, but based on my own recent experience, due to lack of this provision, it would benefit a wide array of people. Sight loss doesn\u2019t mean your life stops.",
        "background": "Make it mandatory for hospitality venues to provide large print and Braille versions of all menus and leaflets.",
